        <UserObject label="" mermaidData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;stateDiagram\n  direction TB\n  [*] --&gt; InitLoading:boot -&gt; add_initproc()\n  InitLoading --&gt; Runnable:发布到 PID2PCB 与调度器\n  Runnable --&gt; Running:调度器选中运行\n  Running --&gt; Runnable:yield / time slice / suspend\n  Running --&gt; Sleeping:wait queue / futex / poll / pipe / socket / wait4 阻塞\n  Sleeping --&gt; Runnable:wakeup_task()\n  Running --&gt; Running:execve()\n  Running --&gt; Forking:clone/fork\n  Forking --&gt; Running:父进程继续执行\n  Forking --&gt; ChildRunnable:子进程发布完成\n  ChildRunnable --&gt; Running:子进程首次被调度\n  Running --&gt; ThreadExit:非主线程 exit\n  ThreadExit --&gt; Running:进程仍存活\n  Running --&gt; ProcZombie:主线程 exit 或 exit_group\n  ProcZombie --&gt; AutoReaped:父进程 SIGCHLD=SIG_IGN 或 SA_NOCLDWAIT\n  AutoReaped --&gt; [*]\n  ProcZombie --&gt; WaitableZombie:等待父进程 wait4/waitpid\n  WaitableZombie --&gt; Reaped:父进程找到 zombie child\n  Reaped --&gt; [*]\n  InitLoading:init / ProcessControlBlock new(\&quot;/sbin/init\&quot;)\nInitLoading:装载 /sbin/init 或 shebang 解释器\nInitLoading:创建 PID、PCB、主线程、用户栈、trap context\nInitLoading:attach_task + insert_into_pid2process + add_task\n\n  Runnable:进程存活\\n主线程 TaskStatus=Runnable\n  Forking:clone_process()\nForking:复制或共享地址空间\nForking:复制 fd/cwd/root/cred/env/sighand 等\nForking:创建子 PCB 与子主线程\nForking:子 trap context 返回值设为 0\n\n  ChildRunnable:子进程已插入 PID2PCB&lt;/br&gt;主线程已 add_task\n  ThreadExit:TaskStatus=Zombie\nThreadExit:清 clear_child_tid / futex / signal wait / timer\n\n  ProcZombie:PCB.is_zombie = true\nProcZombie:记录 ExitReason\nProcZombie:清理 task/fd/shm/timer/用户地址空间\nProcZombie:子进程过继给 INITPROC\nProcZombie:唤醒父进程 wait_exit_queue\n\n  AutoReaped:从 parent.children 移除\nAutoReaped:remove_from_pid2process\n\n  Reaped:编码 wstatus\nReaped:从 children 移除\nReaped:unregister mappings\nReaped:remove_from_pid2process\n\n  note right of Running \n  exec:\n        解析 ELF / shebang\n        替换 memory_set\n        重建主线程用户栈与 trap context\n        保留 PID / parent / children\n        保留未 CLOEXEC 的 fd\n        清空 pending signal\n  end note&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;config&quot;: null&#xa;}" id="7h1SZrtBjEDSIKxkEBlP-1">
